License verification:
=====================
The Licensed Work contains a license verification mechanism in
`shared/licensing/`. This mechanism communicates with the official AICS
Licensing Server to authorize features and enforce license terms.

Demo licenses can be obtained from the AICS Licensing Server at no cost
and grant access to all modules except the on-demand "Gutachten" module
for a limited evaluation period. Production deployments require a
commercial license from the Licensor.

